*ULTRA-MD EXTERNAL PLUGINS:* 

*NOTES:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/a6e6e3679c9e2e2f5cab9a4ce364cb21

  _Description:_ Quickly save your thoughts or reminders. Easily retrieve, Manage your notes by removing outdated or unnecessary ones.


*GET JIDS:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/31a68f74f5483aa3b79a385b7173e558

  _Description:_ Fetches the Jabber ID (JID) of groups and members for easier identification and management.


*R-C STICKER:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/afec1aea0969afeba67cf042efbdf4a0

  _Description:_ Generate stylish rounded corner stickers from images with ease and share them instantly.


*LIVE TIME:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/76e1cfdfc8f7e4e86dad69507ab52c43

  _Description:_ Displays the current live time of any location worldwide, keeping you updated on time zone differences.


*QUOTED STICKER:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/ceea9f82889e287d8cd08508d66bb618

  _Description:_ Create custom text-based stickers, personalized with your own quotes or messages.


*HACK PRANK:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/0004dcf0a605aeb05cbe6a67f4ad2b7f

  _Description:_ A prank tool that simulates a hacking event, perfect for scaring your friends in a fun way.


*LINUX MACHINE:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/9d7fbb6a03fc23fd5574aed7fa6d7237

  _Description:_ Simulates basic Linux machine commands, bringing a virtual Linux environment into WhatsApp chats.


*LEAVE GROUP:*  https://gist.github.com/Guru322/6263ff5478fe20b7467648d694646f6c

  _Description:_ Quickly leave a group with a single command, ideal for situations where you no longer wish to stay.


*CHATBOT:*  https://gist.github.com/Guru322/29b5a553d47b163f187ee840de1d12e8

  _Description:_ Integrate an automated chatbot that engages in meaningful conversations, enhancing user interaction.


*BLACKBOX AI:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/860236d11ba4bf9041d9417b24adc19b

  _Description:_ A sophisticated AI tool designed to analyze data and make predictions using black-box machine learning models.


*TRAVEL ASSISTANT:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/9278ac5e5882289c836374cb40acd06d

  _Description:_ Your personal travel assistant for booking flights, finding hotels, and managing itineraries seamlessly.


*MINIMAL GOOGLE:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/ca6fd6f94a7ea4c64153362ea1eb8f9b

  _Description:_ A minimalistic interface for fast and efficient searches on Google, focusing on speed and simplicity.


*FACTS:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/c5360582b85bc7a2e83c2895b166acf9

  _Description:_ Delivers a random, interesting fact each time you trigger the command, making learning fun and engaging.


*TELL ME:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/3e290cd388192b6b6de0422521de24b3

  _Description:_ Asks random 'Why' questions, sparking thought-provoking conversations and curiosity.


*SEARCH STICKERS:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/35a9d9d01bbc4f6881ce7a6c9de6249a

  _Description:_ Search for stickers by your preferred search term, making it easier to find the perfect sticker for your chat.


*RANDOM WALLP:*  https://gist.github.com/GlobalTechInfo/7b1e0071cb5a6f6ad67ce0ce90746bd5

  _Description:_ Provides random anime-themed wallpapers, allowing you to freshen up your screen with new artwork.
